      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，Deactivated是终态，指向Education Classroom Service。最后在Suspended旁边加个注释，说明账户访问受限。",
